English translation of {{bor|en|ru|Санкт-Петербу́рг}}, from {{der|en|de|[[Sankt]] [[Peter|Peters]][[Burg|burg]]||Saint Peter's City}}, referring to {{w|Saint Peter}} the [[Apostle]] and alluding to its founder [[tsar|Tsar]] {{w|Peter the Great}}.

